# Composto MCP

MCP runs tools. Skill `composto-ir` says when + which LOD layer.

## Reads ‚Äî LOD zoom (L0‚ÜíL1‚ÜíL2‚ÜíL3)

- **L0/L1** first ‚Äî survey + understand
- **L2** ‚Äî what changed (bug/PR)
- **L3** ‚Äî exact source only when needed

`composto_ir` instead of `read_file` unless user wants full raw file.

Multi-file: `composto_context` + `target` + `budget: 4000`.

## Before edits

`composto_blastradius` on `src/`/`lib/`/`app/` files. `high` ‚Üí surface risk.

No `composto_scan`. No `composto_benchmark` unless asked.
